name: RV 8
description:
RV 8 
Its here....Its now...Believe.....Its you....

Raven Vandelle have released 8 Tracks on their latest Disc, including 4 previously unreleased Epics....

Raven Vandelle...
The band is comprised of Dave Taylor (vocals, guitar) and brothers Jimi Crutchley (bass), and Nick Crutchley (guitar). Together, the trio create the unmistakably world class arena crushing rock sound that is Raven Vandelle.

4 Breathe

Dont be the last to know.................


RV 8 was produced by Nick Mailing at Lost Boys Studios in Cranfield Bedfordshire.. roosterhenhouse@live.com
